      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive away in a vehicle that truly stands out! This car is in good condition and has been clearly well-maintained, offering a reliable and smooth performance you can count on. It looks sharp and is ready for many more miles of dependable service\u2014perfect for anyone looking for quality and style at a great value!",
