    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine is strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, ensuring a reliable driving experience for its next owner. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal use, the car remains very clean and mechanically sound. It\u2019s an excellent choice for anyone seeking a dependable, high-quality vehicle without the brand-new price tag.",
      "price": 33500.0,
