      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of uncompromising standards. This specimen maintains a showroom-caliber aesthetic, reflecting a history of meticulous preservation and mechanical excellence. Every surface and component adheres to the highest tier of automotive refinement, offering the discerning buyer a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine asset. We invite serious inquiries to experience this peerless example firsthand.",
      "price": 48900.0,
